{"tid":939284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【凱滙開售】觀塘街坊李生：對觀塘區有感情 　呎價3萬都會買","createTime":"2018-12-13T03:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T06:19:51.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"72f8694293d2197f3531620c822d27bd591e7bea","tid":939284,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2203371/org/de1223dd909e6c67ca07455b3f6e41e7.jpg/MYqqqW8lsD20DzKd4EPhamblNkmZyLUIpK22MaSttjE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2203371%2Forg%2Fde1223dd909e6c67ca07455b3f6e41e7.jpg%2FMYqqqW8lsD20DzKd4EPhamblNkmZyLUIpK22MaSttjE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=cac474b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n信置（0083）等牽頭發展的觀塘凱匯今日開售，買家李先生表示，已斥1,000萬元買入兩房單位作收租用途。他指自己是觀塘老街坊，對該區有感情，已居住28年。而他等待是次重建項目落成已有10年，並指新盤「幾錢都會買，（呎價）3萬元都買」。他透露自己從事物流業，收入有6位數字。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2203374/org/1b697851076bb4777cf8e8e2e7b066aa.jpg/-_P0_iixDVbH0eTxEA8bM3r-0lmPXAqHvfkhRr35IUY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2203374%2Forg%2F1b697851076bb4777cf8e8e2e7b066aa.jpg%2F-_P0_iixDVbH0eTxEA8bM3r-0lmPXAqHvfkhRr35IUY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=707cb058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭籌買家李生、李太表示雖然新樓樓花期較長，但有信心屆時樓價會升。（林樂謙攝）<br />\n<br />\n從事地產行業的頭籌買家李生、李太表示，已斥資1,600萬元買入高層3房單位自住，形容該單位景觀好。李太指觀塘地區交通便利，海邊有不少甲級寫字樓，亦方便未來上班。她表示有比較過同區2手單位，而該新盤開價吸引。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2203377/org/d0f51e4eaef1659e0ac79187a3cdb430.jpg/fKqCJkhQ13AE0GvPVdNHuGcagdjCa0Bn_xe0Rf8XtEU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2203377%2Forg%2Fd0f51e4eaef1659e0ac79187a3cdb430.jpg%2FfKqCJkhQ13AE0GvPVdNHuGcagdjCa0Bn_xe0Rf8XtEU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1bedbf30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買家溫小姐認為新盤開價便宜，已斥約700萬元作為首期。（林樂謙攝）<br />\n<br />\n另一位買家溫小姐剛以1,400萬元買入3房中層單位自住，她指新盤「價格好誠意，估唔到開價咁平，今次抽中好有緣分。」她已斥約700萬元作為首期，又指曾在觀塘區上班，交通方便。"},{"pid":"cc5981aca6a79ee899afcce244d702cba07519f9","tid":939284,"uid":38772,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"叫開觀塘雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afba175c6f16137239f82ee767acc3f8eb55136","tid":939284,"uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:53:43.000Z","msg":"Actor"},{"pid":"2ab67ac251c2a754d6ce276f728ea5068f770eb7","tid":939284,"uid":214036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e58f678ae71ccfbdfba7a742a7c7583656b2c13","tid":939284,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:57:57.000Z","msg":"李生李太<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf2401a95a52fc9504df2d6e3c06e0a05a88aec","tid":939284,"uid":30247,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"而家d人做媒做到咁誇張既"},{"pid":"c70e4bca0c4036f0fd5d0008329bf0753ac5651f","tid":939284,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"識野<br />\n<br />\n專家都係食屎就岩"},{"pid":"3730c2f949166ae1ed67e126135246c98fd9b918","tid":939284,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"感情無價😭<br />\n30萬呎照殺😍"},{"pid":"960956010aa9558236597e01e07bf6e889b218cd","tid":939284,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"他透露自己從事物流業，<span style=\"color: red;\">年</span>收入有6位數字<br />\n記者係咪打少字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa